1. On će *preuzeti* dužnosti direktora od ponedeljka. (He will *take over* the duties of the director starting from Monday.) 
2. Nadam se da će firma *preuzeti* ovaj projekat i završiti ga na vreme. (I hope the company will *take on* this project and complete it on time.)
3. Nakon smene, novi menadžment će *preuzeti* kontrolu nad kompanijom. (After the change, the new management will *take control* of the company.)
4. Organizator je rekao da će *preuzeti* odgovornost za neuspeh događaja. (The organizer said he would *take responsibility* for the failure of the event.)
5. Možeš li mi *preuzeti* ovaj paket dok sam na poslu? (Can you *pick up* this package for me while I'm at work?)
6. Kada *preuzmeš* firmu, imaćeš veliku odgovornost. (When you *take over* the company, you will have a great responsibility.)
7. Očekuje se da će novi premijer *preuzeti* dužnost sledećeg meseca. (The new prime minister is expected to *assume* office next month.)
8. Nisam siguran ko će *preuzeti* mesto šefa odeljenja. (I'm not sure who will *take up* the position of department head.)